data.name: chkSettingsDownloadsFixVReddIt.ToolTip
data.value:
Fixes visual corruptions on v.redd.it/reddit.com links using ffmpeg's HTTP Live Streaming (HLS)
Recommended to stay on. This requires FFMPEG to be installed and available, it will fallback to youtube-dl's default.

data.name: chkSettingsDownloadsSeparateDownloadsToDifferentFolders.ToolTip
data.value:
Separates downloads into their own folder based on the download type
Videos would be <download directory>\Video Audio would be <download directory>\Audio Custom would be <download directory>\Custom

data.name: numConvertVideoBitrate.ToolTip
data.value:
The bitrate of the video
A bitrate is how many bits per second are streamed to the player
higher = better, at the cost of file size
If you were to input "10,000" as the bitrate, it would be interpreted as "10,000,000" bits per second.
